-- Euro Gains Before Merkel-Lagarde Meeting
-- B y   C a n d i c e   Z a c h a r i a h s
-- 2012-01-10T06:16:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-10/euro-advances-for-second-day-before-merkel-lagarde-meet-on-debt-crisis.html
The euro gained for a second day
before  Germany ’s chancellor and the International
Monetary Fund’s managing director meet amid optimism  Europe ’s
leaders are taking steps to resolve the debt crisis.  The 17-nation currency advanced 0.2 percent to $1.2795 as
of 6:15 a.m. in  London , and strengthened 0.2 percent to 98.26
yen.  To contact the reporter on this story:
